Lingua::KOR::Num2Word — Korean number to word conversion
Lingua::KOR::Num2Word — 숫자를 한국어 수사로 변환

Converts numbers into their Korean cardinal text representation.
Part of the PetaMem Lingua number conversion suite.

SYNOPSIS

    use Lingua::Num2Word qw(cardinal);
    my $text = cardinal('ko', 42);

INSTALLATION

    shell> cpanm Lingua::KOR::Num2Word

    or install all available languages at once:

    shell> cpanm Task::Lingua::PetaMem

SUPPORTED RANGE

    Integers from 0 to 999,999,999.

SEE ALSO

    Lingua::KOR::Word2Num — the reverse direction
    Lingua::Num2Word      — multi-language number-to-word wrapper
    Lingua::Word2Num      — multi-language word-to-number wrapper
    Task::Lingua::PetaMem — install all languages

